Dear members of the credit derivatives group.


You've probably been wondering if I would ever get the minutes of last weeks

meeting out. Well, here they are and I sincerely apologize for the delay. I

always thought this time of year is supposed to be slow, but unfortunately,

the opposite has been the case.


Please pay particular attention to the action points. We can only handle

these meetings successfully if each and everyone of you actively

participates and plays a role! The next meeting can only be scheduled if

there is enough feedback available.


Wishing you happy holidays,


Regards,


